{
  "texts": [
    "However, each following redaction attempts to perform the same type of operation on the text, even after identifying information has been removed.",
    "The repetition of this operation leads to increasing abstraction and generality in the text.",
    "For example, in the second redaction, some of the changes are listed as Specific actions and gestures are generalized.",
    "For example, \"held the bowl aloft and intoned\" has been replaced with \"held the object aloft and intoned\", and \"made rapid crosses in the air\" has been replaced with \"made motions in the air\".",
    "In the third redaction, these actions and gestures are 'further obfuscated': Actions and Gestures: Specific actions were further generalized."
  ]
}